      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 12.5,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "• each thread reads 8 elements\n   (4 from A, 4 from B)\n• 16 threads × 8 = 128 total reads\n• A has only 16 unique elements,\n   B has 16\n→ each element read many times",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• each thread reads 8 elements\n   (4 from A, 4 from B)\n• 16 threads × 8 = 128 total reads\n• A has only 16 unique elements,\n   B has 16\n→ each element read many times",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
