      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 12.5,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "• each thread reads 2048 elements\n   (1024 from A + 1024 from B)\n• 1,048,576 threads × 2048\n   = 2.1 billion reads\n• only 1,048,576 unique each\n→ massive redundancy",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• each thread reads 2048 elements\n   (1024 from A + 1024 from B)\n• 1,048,576 threads × 2048\n   = 2.1 billion reads\n• only 1,048,576 unique each\n→ massive redundancy",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
